ZH: 太平之世，人人都能安居乐业。
EN: In times of peace, everyone can live and work in peace.

ZH: 太平盛世，百姓生活幸福安稳。
EN: In a peaceful and prosperous era, the people live a happy and stable life.

ZH: 太平时期，战争不再肆虐。
EN: During times of peace, war no longer ravages.

ZH: 太平年代，人们心情愉快。
EN: In a peaceful era, people have a cheerful mood.

ZH: 天下太平，百姓安康。
EN: When there is peace throughout the land, the people are healthy and safe.

ZH: 太平如日，社会风气祥和。
EN: When there is peace like the sun, the social atmosphere is harmonious.

ZH: 他一生都向往太平安宁。
EN: He has always longed for peace and tranquility in his life.

ZH: 只有太平社会，人们才能实现自己的梦想。
EN: Only in a peaceful society can people achieve their dreams.

ZH: 每个人都希望生活过得太平安逸。
EN: Everyone hopes to live a peaceful and comfortable life.

ZH: 孩子们在太平时期长大，少了许多磨难。
EN: Children grow up in peaceful times, with fewer hardships.

ZH: 希望我们的国家永远都是太平富裕。
EN: I hope our country will always be peaceful and prosperous.

ZH: 在太平年代，文化艺术得以繁荣发展。
EN: In peaceful times, culture and the arts flourish.

ZH: 太平盛世，国家强大而稳定。
EN: In a peaceful and prosperous era, the country is strong and stable.

ZH: 战争带来的苦难让人更加珍惜太平时光。
EN: The suffering brought by war makes people cherish peaceful times even more.

ZH: 只有太平社会才能迎来繁荣和发展。
EN: Only in a peaceful society can prosperity and development be achieved.

ZH: 在太平时期，人们更加关注文化和教育的发展。
EN: In peaceful times, people pay more attention to the development of culture and education.

ZH: 太平的国家吸引着越来越多的外国投资。
EN: A peaceful country attracts more and more foreign investment.

ZH: 太平之年，人民迎接着富裕的生活。
EN: In a peaceful era, the people embrace a prosperous life.

ZH: 太平之世，社会风气淳朴善良。
EN: In a peaceful world, society is characterized by simplicity and kindness.

ZH: 每个人都希望生活在一个太平安稳的环境中。
EN: Everyone hopes to live in a peaceful and stable environment.
